<% title '' %>

<div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">

      <form class="js_route" action="/">

        <h1 class="heading-large">Appeal to the tax tribunal</h1>

        <p>The tax tribunal is run by the Ministry of Justice.</p>
        <p>Try and settle your dispute directly first. If you can't, a judge will make an impartial decision on your case.</p>
        <p>Use this service to submit an appeal or close an enquiry into your tax affairs. You can start an appeal and come back to submit details later.</p>
        
        <h2 class="heading-medium">What you will need</h2>
        <p>You'll need:</p>
        <ul class="list list-bullet">
        <li>a scan or photo of your original notice or review conclusion letter</li>
        <li>reasons for your appeal so the judge can hear things from your side</li>
      </ul>

      <p>You'll also need to complete an <a href="<%= asset_path('proforma.pdf') %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">authorisation form (PDF, 241KB)<span class="visuallyhidden"> (opens in new window)</span></a></strong> if you want someone to represent you and they are not a practising solicitor or barrister.</p>

      <% if !save_and_return_enabled? %>

      <h2 class="notice util_mt-large">
        <i class="icon icon-important">
          <span class="visuallyhidden">Warning</span>
        </i>
        <strong class="bold-small">
          You can't save details so get everything ready before you start
        </strong>
      </h2>

      <% end %>

      <p>
        <%= link_to 'Start now', start_path, class: 'button' %>
      </p>
      <h2 class="heading-medium">Other ways to apply</h2>
      <p>You can apply by post. Download and fill in:</p>
      <ul class="list list-bullet">
        <li>a <a class="external" rel="external" href="http://hmctsformfinder.justice.gov.uk/HMCTS/GetForm.do?court_forms_id=3015">notice of appeal (T240)</a> to submit an appeal</li>
        <li>an <a class="external" rel="external" href="http://hmctsformfinder.justice.gov.uk/HMCTS/GetForm.do?court_forms_id=3019">application to close an enquiry (T245)</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>The address is on the form.</p>
      </form>

    </div>

    <div class="column-one-third">
      <aside class="govuk-related-items">

        <h2 class="heading-medium">Courts, sentencing and tribunals</h2>
